I offered her a ten-spot.

501
00:29:06,082 --> 00:29:07,682
Yeah, but she wouldn't have it.

502
00:29:07,683 --> 00:29:10,483
She's no dummy!
She can add!

503
00:29:10,484 --> 00:29:14,984
Why take a tenner today when
you can get 62.50 every week?

504
00:29:14,985 --> 00:29:18,185
Oh, Bud, the only thing you've got
against her is where she works.

505
00:29:18,786 --> 00:29:21,176
You've got the kid all wrong.
The only reason she works there...

506
00:29:21,177 --> 00:29:23,500
...is because she needs a lot
of money to help her folks.

507
00:29:23,701 --> 00:29:26,151
So that's the racket, huh?

508
00:29:26,152 --> 00:29:28,352
The mother needs an operation.

509
00:29:28,353 --> 00:29:30,423
The kid brother's gotta have
his eyes treated...

510
00:29:30,424 --> 00:29:31,524
Oh, nothing like it.

511
00:29:31,525 --> 00:29:35,400
I don't doubt she makes a lot of money but
I bet she don't make it all by dancing.

512
00:29:38,001 --> 00:29:39,881
Now listen, Bud.

513
00:29:39,882 --> 00:29:42,442
Even when you say that
I don't get sore.

514
00:29:42,443 --> 00:29:45,043
