bureau ain't going out of business.

537
00:30:39,602 --> 00:30:41,802
Yeah, well it ain't gonna get
any of my trade.

538
00:30:41,803 --> 00:30:43,103
Not yet anyway.

539
00:30:43,104 --> 00:30:47,304
