572
00:32:51,901 --> 00:32:54,801
- Let's stay and see that.
- No, it ain't gonna be any good.

573
00:32:56,402 --> 00:32:59,202
Nobody's any good in here.

574
00:33:00,103 --> 00:33:02,803
They're just flies.

575
00:33:02,804 --> 00:33:06,904
- I want another drink.
- Say, you've had enough already.

576
00:33:08,305 --> 00:33:11,605
A girl like you oughtn't to drink
all the stuff you do.

577
00:33:11,606 --> 00:33:14,406
I have to. It makes me
forget my troubles.

578
00:33:15,707 --> 00:33:18,000
